rows.label: tev078901_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Toluera about the other Zaruboggan.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078901_MSG0001
rows.name:
They spend their lives fulfilling the calling given to them
by Golboggaâ€”the calling of devoltanizing and
purifying their planet. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078901_MSG0002
rows.name:
And that is all they have done for who-knows how
many eons. *fsssh* They are a race of fools![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078901_MSG0003
rows.name:
And you're as much of a fool as any of them for
buying into their idiocy instead of accepting the truth
of my words! *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078901_MSG0008
rows.name:
I cannot live with humans who have been so thoroughly
duped by such Golbogga fanatics. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078901_MSG0009
rows.name:
So if the time comes where I can no longer live here
on my own, I suppose I will go and surrender to the
Ganglion. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078901_MSG0010
rows.name:
I doubt they would kill me if I offered my complete
obedience. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078901_MSG0011
rows.name:
And if, theoretically, they end up eradicating all
of the Zaruboggan that have allied with humanity...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078901_MSG0012
rows.name:
then I will have avenged myself against all of the
fools who repudiated my theories! *fsssh*[ST:wait ]
